metadata.description: The Etherminati NFT collection is a unique and exclusive group of non-fungible tokens that offer membership to an exclusive secret society. Each NFT in the collection holds all the information necessary for your membership badge, including your new secret society identity. This NFT collection provides access to exclusive events, perks, and benefits that only members of the Etherminati can enjoy. The NFTs in this collection are one-of-a-kind, ensuring that only a select few will have access to the benefits of the secret society. Become a member of the Etherminati and join the ranks of the chosen few who hold the power of a coveted NFT membership.
